Spin, spin, spin...

750
00:53:42,784 --> 00:53:45,784
あ、髪の毛可愛い！髪の毛ふわふわで可愛い！
Ah, the hair is cute! It's so fluffy and cute!

751
00:53:45,784 --> 00:53:49,284
ふわふわだよ！髪型めちゃ可愛い！え、お姫様！
It's fluffy! The hairstyle is super cute! Like a princess!

